{BOLD}{YELLOW}A Path Into a Dense Forest{bold}{yellow}~
{G}
   You and  your  companions feel as if
   you have been traveling for days and
   days, although the sky remains dark,
   and  the forest  desolate and absent
   of any sign of life.

   After you all stop for camp you hear
   crunching of twigs and what seems to
   be  the   sound  of  whispering, but
   shrug it off as a delusion.

   You  have stayed on  the path, which
   is  to  lead to  the  mountains that
   guard  the  valley of  NeXis, but it
   seems  as  though  you  are going in
   circles.  The  winter  is   cold  in
   these parts, and  it is obvious that
   a blizzard is fast approaching. 
