{BOLD}{YELLOW}NeXis Market Square{bold}{yellow}~
{BOLD}{YELLOW}
   You have arrived in the NeXis town square. Despite the disasters
   which have taken place here,  the folk seem to have continued life
   as usual. You see people of all classes and occupations bustling
   around you, dropping parcels, and luggage as they go.

   You think to yourself, something is amiss here. These people are
   not shopping or heading to work, they are leaving the city, you
   notice now that what you thought was a brisk walk, is a desperate
   run. All around you people trip over one another, some being
   squished under the masses. 

   You hear wails and screams, human and not so human.

   You draw your sword from its hilt and  prepare for combat!
