{BOLD,BLACK}The Drunken Dog{bold,black}~
{BOLD,BLACK}
   The Drunken Dog, a typical dockside tavern if ever there was one, is the
   most squalid, insalubrious alehouse you have encountered in NeXis. Its
   windows, broken time and time again in countless brawls, have been
   nailed over with a clumsy patchwork of boards, and the taproom stinks of
   smoke and grease and unwashed bodies. The floor is slick underfoot, a
   vile morass of sawdust, spilled drink - and, more often then not, blood.
   Right now, the river is low, so the air is thick with the noxious stench of
   dead fish and sewage. 
{bold,black}
